{"type": "article", "id": 43713, "title": "为了推广无现金日，微信做了个“钱味”香氛 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2017-08-03T04:46:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 30946, "name": "无现金"}, {"id": 66, "name": "Facebook"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 13, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170803110520TKSbmXkMYF1U4HoC.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一说的广告</h3><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://www.digitaling.com/articles/38862.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">苏宁易购为 818 购物节促销做的新广告，眼熟么</a>？</b>又一个互联网公司的“大字报”户外广告，但这到底在说啥啊？<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170803113107rQkcHTpM32nAh4ZO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170803113129Cnh5Ss3FgwQf7WjE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><b><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NjM4MDAxMg==&amp;mid=2655075565&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=0632057e87ad6351f4f618cf76aef25a&amp;chksm=bd5fb0ee8a2839f890e67b4954e62ca3e99f4b2a68dfc38436919ad9c4e73d6a8c66b38b05b9&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0802Ojb9aGadghEL6nccgaFr&amp;key=9d7a2a43293777bcdea0af5a4ae93f931b18c2ec19bbb9c1612cfd772016dcd65aa42a073300209c15add98142b638df56b425590d3f45ac3539e7ca713278914386abcf22cb772727a6eca741d92b45&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MTIyNTYzODY0MA%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir6%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.10.5+build(14F2511)&amp;version=11000006&amp;pass_ticket=5LaVT%2BqA1F8i%2BTKD1th0Htgr5YpvDHyuHOEyEDf1V6Zp493ZUaTTUUj8FwW5rM7K\" rel=\"nofollow\">为造势 “8.8 无现金日”，微信支付团队推出了“钱”味香氛。</a></b>点赞数最高的十条留言可拿。我们猜银行工作人员不会想参与。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170803112316HECZSvVTgiQ0yJzG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"webp\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170803112306VOoWDLbqCH8lZpM7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.803125\" data-format=\"webp\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UbBBkyoMknY\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>英国电信服务商&nbsp;Three UK 拍了一个很诡异的广告片</b></a>，手机“瘾君子”在指导下像邪教组织一样在做朝拜，祈求看更多视频。在手机上看这支广告，挺讽刺的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170803114133YXdlDkeyVFH7I0aM.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.506250\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>公司有啥大事发生</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/08/02/tmall-luxury-channel-launched-the-first-batch-of-burberry-lvmh-maserati-and-so-on/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>天猫奢侈品频道 Luxury Pavilion 上线</b></a>，但据说只有在天猫平台上购买过奢侈品或者部分超级 88 会员才可见。另外该平台将实行品牌定向邀约制，即限量对品牌开放。首批入驻天猫奢侈品牌包括 Burberry、Hugo boss、海蓝之谜、玛莎拉蒂、娇兰、真力时等。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MTI1OTA1Mg==&amp;mid=2649674170&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=03c7383af961a9803d81e6dad842f22e&amp;chksm=872a3779b05dbe6fd9b3da3eca62792ab3a582e7267fb686aef8facf2b144d3d60eda3440aa1&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0803vGit30a2FhN9vSqYlZF5&amp;key=9ca90f9c8509714f893011fe43d18de526c34c03f4830f4be955fb8ead5a4dc48aaed9901ad21e8f832596501fc2ca4a3935add73c93ff706c2780cb6b4efd5d725f664068c28336d191b124c7a81185&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MTIyNTYzODY0MA%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir6%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.10.5+build(14F2511)&amp;version=11000006&amp;pass_ticket=5LaVT%2BqA1F8i%2BTKD1th0Htgr5YpvDHyuHOEyEDf1V6Zp493ZUaTTUUj8FwW5rM7K\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Facebook 发布用户使用时长数据。</b></a>年龄在 25 岁以下的 Instagram 用户日均使用时间为 32 分钟，25 岁以上为 24 分钟。Stories 功能的日均用户数为 2.5 亿。<br></p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.adquan.com/post-3-41695.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>华扬联众数字技术股份有限公司（Hylink）8 月 2 日 正式在上海证券交易所挂牌上市。</b></a><br></p><p><b><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/08/02/hillknowlton-strategies-is-appointed-as-wanda-groups-first-global-pr-agency/\" rel=\"nofollow\">伟达公关（Hill+Knowlton Strategies）成为大连万达集团（Dalian Wanda Group）首个全球性公关代理公司。</a></b></p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/08/02/infiniti-names-72andsunny-as-global-creative-agency-of-record-without-a-review/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>日产汽车旗下豪车品牌英菲尼迪（Infiniti）将其全球创意业务交由创意代理机构 72andSunny 打理。</b></a><br></p><h3>还有些你可能想知道的数字</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.adquan.com/post-2-41696.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>CTR 媒介智讯发布数据</b></a>，2017 上半年广告市场整体刊例花费增长 0.4%，传统广告下降 4.1%。宝洁依然是传统广告花费最多的公司。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170803115158JpUNEi9M4GPwtKY7.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.565588\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://tech.qq.com/a/20170802/034193.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>高德开放平台与乐铺达成战略合作，发布北京街区流量价值排行报告</b></a>。五道营胡同、工体北路、团结湖路拿下工作日日均道路人流排行 TOP3；而工体北路、团结湖路、朝外南街则排行节假日日均道路人流前三名。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170803115404OerZaRAvjSH0qKdJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.535433\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">题图来源：<a href=\"http://blog.oxforddictionaries.com/2014/08/bread-cheese-dough-come-mean-money/\" rel=\"nofollow\">oxforddictionaries</a></p><style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 25.0px 0.0px; line-height: 35.0px; font: 30.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #ffffff; background-color: #eeeeee} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>"}